# DPD Control Tower — Architecture (living reference)

> **Maintain this file.** Append to **Change log** on every structural change. Tag entries `[admin+app]` when mobile handoff must update too.

**Product:** Enterprise rider workforce Control Tower (Musallam / DPD).  
**Admin:** Next.js 16 · `dpdadmin/` · https://dpdadmin.vercel.app  
**Driver app:** Separate repo/session — paste [`docs/DRIVER_APP_HANDOFF.md`](../docs/DRIVER_APP_HANDOFF.md)  
**Backend:** Supabase `ytfmsgckjatiserpgdbz` (Postgres + Auth + Storage + Realtime)

---

## System context

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  DriverApp["Driver App mobile"] -->|"OTP auth, deliveries, requests, chat"| Supabase["Supabase"]
  AdminPanel["Admin Panel web"] -->|"verify, approve, monitor"| Supabase
  Partners["Talabat / DoorDash / UberEats"] -->|"external orders"| DriverApp
  Supabase -->|"realtime"| AdminPanel
  Supabase -->|"push"| DriverApp
```

Order allocation is **external** (partner apps). We own: monitoring, compliance, payroll, support.

