## UI conventions

- Design: `design-system/dpd-admin/TOKENS.md`, `COMPONENTS.md`
- List pages: `<ModuleListShell>` = PageHeader + KpiGrid + TabBar + DataTableShell
- Theme tokens only — no raw hex
- Table headers: `text-xs font-semibold text-accent`
- i18n: `en` + `ar`, keys under `pages.<module>`

